Global Securities Brokerages And Stock Exchanges Market Insights
Securities Brokerages And Stock Exchanges Market size was valued at USD 69 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 95 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Securities Brokerages And Stock Exchanges Market Overview
The global securities brokerages and stock exchanges market is valued at approximately USD 60.2 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a CAGR of 4.2% during the forecast period (2024-2028). The market growth is attributed to the increasing demand for investment solutions, technological advancements in trading platforms, and rising adoption of digital tools. The Asia-Pacific region leads the market in terms of trading volumes, while North America holds a significant share in terms of market value. The market dynamics are influenced by key players in the brokerage and exchange sectors, offering a variety of financial instruments and services to retail and institutional investors.

